---
title: Middle Eastern Chicken and Halloumi Dinner with Chopped Salad and Lentil-Rice Pilaf
description: Tender chicken cooked with yogurt sauce and warming Shawarma Spice Blend is the perfect complement to Mudajara-inspired lentil-and-rice pilaf. Seared halloumi and a fresh chopped veggie salad completes the meal.
